title: Glenn Miller Orchestra - In The Christmas Mood Volume II
description:
Source: 1993 CD

Glenn Miller Orchestra - In The Christmas Mood Volume II 320cbr (Big Papi) 1993 1930s-40s Music 






By A Customer
This CD will carry you away to the Christmas memories you have of the late 30's and early 40's. All of the Miller greats are featured in stirring solos, the arrangements are great; if you are in any way a fan of the big bands you should get this one. Five stars plus+
